  The multiplicative group object $\mathbb G_m = \mathbb A^1 \setminus \{0\}$ described in
  \cref{def:genus0_base_objects}, packaged as an object of $\mathrm{Over}\,(\Spec \bar k)$.
\end{definition}

\begin{definition}
